name: Fluxbot Plugins
body:
## So, you want to do more with your fluxbot?
You've come to the right place. Below, you'll find a list of plugins you can download now, pop in your plugins folder and run!


***
* [bf.js](https://gist.github.com/whiskers75/9112248) - brainf**k interpreter for fluxbot
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
